Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.40,0:01:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是裤头村一个非常特别的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is a very special day in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了  我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我知识助记卡片你带了没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, did you bring my flashcards?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.18,0:01:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带了呢  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right here, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.34,0:01:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,过驾考要用到的所有知识都在卡片上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.34,0:01:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything you need to pass the test is on these cards
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.97,0:01:20.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:20.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,学习的味道真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Learning tastes good
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.72,0:01:24.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我还得用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:24.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I needed those
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.47,0:01:25.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:25.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fiddlesticks
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你驾考考的次数比谁都多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've taken that driving test more times than anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都57次了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.52,0:01:29.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,57 times
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那58就是你的幸运数字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well then, 58 is your lucky number
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.54,0:01:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾考你非过不可  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're gonna pass that driving test, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you're a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.21,0:01:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是大赢家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a winner?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a winner?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.12,0:01:39.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:39.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a winner?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.57,0:01:44.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's a winner?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.00,0:01:44.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是大赢家
