Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a winner, I'm a winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:47.33,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(472,616)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.33,0:01:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,一分三十七秒后
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考得怎么样  大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you do, winner?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾照给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see that license
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.29,0:02:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾照没考到  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.29,0:02:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't get a license, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾照到时候是要邮寄给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are they gonna mail it to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我驾考挂科了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I failed the boating test
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到头来58并不是我的幸运数字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess 58 wasn't my lucky number, after all
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.87,0:02:10.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:10.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No way
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,58可是史上最幸运的数字了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:13.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,58 is, like, the luckiest number ever
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这驾考一定有暗箱操作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The test must be rigged
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是回家吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's just go home, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没查明白  就哪都别想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not goin' anywhere until I get to the bottom of this
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要亲自来考试
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.67,0:02:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm takin' that test myself
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.56,0:02:22.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:22.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经练了好多年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:24.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been training for years
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们会生吞你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They'll eat you alive
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:28.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很清楚自己在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.42,0:02:30.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I know what I'm doing
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:35.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.54,0:02:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别想评判我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not the judge of me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我考官当然得评判了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, I am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.85,0:02:42.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考试现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:42.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the testing begin
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不该让他考的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have let him do it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还算什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of friend am I?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在你身边  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:48.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here for you, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我驾考过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I passed my test
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是满分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:52.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a perfect score?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是说过很难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you said it was hard
Dialogue: 1,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,score
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:02:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.48,0:03:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得给我的新驾照去拍证件照了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've gotta get my picture taken for my new license
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站在线后面  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:05.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stand behind the line, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我样子如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:06.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do I look?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.51,0:03:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,像个大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.51,0:03:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Like a winner
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.16,0:03:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.67,0:03:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.67,0:03:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:25.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,394)}恭喜
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你  派大星先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Mr. Star
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是第一百万个通过驾考的考生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the one-millionth person to pass the test
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.75,0:03:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以是不是要送免费钥匙链给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.75,0:03:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I get a free key chain?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.87,0:03:23.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:23.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要送你一辆全新汽船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You get a brand-new boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.64,0:03:31.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全新炸鲈三千终极汽船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The new bass blaster 3000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the ultimate boating machine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, all right
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,美女会想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Women will want you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帅哥会想成为你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Men will want to be you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友都会嫉妒你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll be the envy of your friends
Dialogue: 1,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我考到了驾照  赢到了新船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got my license and a new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:49.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:51.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,happy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喇叭能响
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horn works
Dialogue: 1,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天简直是史上最棒的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest day ever
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:02.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,right, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.43,0:04:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本想不出能让今天好转的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't think of one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that would make this day better
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考到驾照那个不算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Except maybe getting my license
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是你亲自去考的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you apply yourself
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.15,0:04:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就有可能刚好第两百万个考到驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you could be the two-millionth person
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to get his license
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第两百万
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two-millionth?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就有可能跟我一样免费领新船了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then you could get a free boat, just like me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.12,0:04:20.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对对  就跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.12,0:04:20.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, "just like you"
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想激励别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I try to serve as an inspiration to others
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还回不回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we go home now?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都已经绕着你家开好几小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've been drivin' around your house for hours
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:27.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比走路快上个不少呢  对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a lot faster than walking, isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送我一程  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:32.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正你也只能当个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.60,0:04:34.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't help being a
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.66,0:04:35.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pedestrian
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要修我船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to work on my boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能给我小点声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, could you keep it down?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在凌晨三点  别人还得睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.57,0:05:01.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's 3:00 in the morning, people are trying to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都四点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:06.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,4:00
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个点了谁在按门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:10.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who could be at the door at this-
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:11.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wha-
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎么了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what is it, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对猜不到我今天怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will never guess what happened to me today
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你考到驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:18.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got your license?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.71,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(204,386)}裤头村驾照\N派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:21.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that's not all
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你领到了新船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.13,0:05:23.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:23.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不会一直在跟踪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you been followin' me?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管好你自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:28.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, you need to get your own life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想睡上个几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just need a few minutes sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的新船我都看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I saw his new boat
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So tired
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  要搭便船上班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, need a ride to work?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.92,0:05:48.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我宁愿走路去上班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.77,0:05:50.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but I'd rather walk to work
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:53.70,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(466,336)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.70,0:05:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来没驾照的生活有那么空虚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, I never realized how empty life is without a license
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多谢你送我一程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the ride
Dialogue: 1,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.87,0:06:04.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等你考到驾照就能送我一程了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:04.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can give me rides once you get your license
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该说是  假如你考到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:06.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, if you get your license
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了  再也不坐派大星开的船了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, I am through driving around with Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是再让我看到一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I have to see one more boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你负责接得来速的单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, you're mannin' the drive-through
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥时候开的得来速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When did we get a drive-through?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.02,0:06:20.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现最近不少小年轻都忙个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I realize there's a lot of young people
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"on the go" these days
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没空好好坐下好好吃一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:22.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't have time to sit down and eat
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而是忙着行驶在开阔的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're too busy, out on the open road
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活出自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,livin' their dreams
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前也有过梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:29.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used to have a dream
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.13,0:06:29.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:29.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以前还得过肾结石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I used to have a kidney stone
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切总都会过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.42,0:06:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything passes eventually
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别做白日梦了  工作谋生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.02,0:06:35.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, stop dreamin', and work for a livin'
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临蟹堡王  我可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Krusty Krab, may I-
Dialogue: 1,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喇叭还能响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The horn still works
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:43.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,766)}开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:44.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(710,766)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛戴头盔  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.95,0:06:49.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's with the helmet, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我既然已经是个专业司机了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:51.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, since I'm now an expert driver
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就得好好改造一下形象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to keep up my image
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  开船可真简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, driving is so easy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我教你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to give you lessons?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That would be great
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:07.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.32,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1238,268)}公交
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈妈好  爸爸好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, mommy, hi, daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  得跟你说多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, how many times do we have to tell you?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是海绵宝宝的爸妈  不是你爸妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're SpongeBob's mom and dad, not yours
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来我是孤儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:17.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm an orphan?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过猜怎么着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:19.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But guess what
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(806,250)}裤头村驾照\N派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我驾考过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I passed my driver's test
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.26,0:07:25.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝又挂科了  千万别提那事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:25.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob failed his test, so don't mention it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们很会避雷的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We know how to stay clear of that minefield
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要带走路宝宝回家去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I've gotta take Mr. Walks-a-lot back home
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他老是找我搭便船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.47,0:07:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's always askin' for rides
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连派大星都能考到驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:39.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even Patrick has a license
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看这宝贝能干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see what this baby can do
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:47.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,236)}限速{\fnArial}40{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}迈
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这边限速40迈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, the speed limit is 40 miles per hour
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.85,0:07:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对对对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:53.04,0:07:55.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四十迈半了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:55.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forty-and-a-half miles per hour
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快41迈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's almost 41 miles per hour
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他超速了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:58.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's speeding
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:00.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop this car
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.23,0:08:03.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:03.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.83,0:08:04.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:04.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,who?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警官  我要尽自己的公民义务
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Officer, it is my civic duty
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,举报这艘船的司机超速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to report that the driver of this vehicle is speeding
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快用测速枪测他速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you clock him with your radar gun?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:11.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他其实才开了40迈  没超速
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Actually, he's going 40 miles under the limit
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这打小报告的快滚  不然抓你坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So move along before I run you in, tattletale
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定不抓他坐牢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't wanna run him in?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是红灯  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a red light, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你都连闯三个红灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:32.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just ran three red lights
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.92,0:08:33.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:33.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该停船才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:35.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to stop
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.63,0:08:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才司机很清楚自己在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.63,0:08:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think the driving genius knows what he's doing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才司机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:41.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Driving genius?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天才会非法调头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Would a genius make an illegal u-turn?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会飙进孤儿院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Through an orphanage?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面的人早及时逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They ran for it in time
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你气什么气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you so mad about?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,考到驾照的应该是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:50.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should've gotten that license
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这船应该是我的才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this should be my boatmobile
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么能这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you were my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我考到驾照就得为我高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'd be happy for me getting my license
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you were my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不会拿你驾照怼我脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't rub your license in my face
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才没拿我驾照怼你脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.95,0:09:05.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not rubbing my license in your face
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫拿我驾照怼你脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is rubbing my license in your face
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:16.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一生努力奋斗就为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've worked my whole life for this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你根本就不配
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't deserve this
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱扔垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Litterbugs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我才要担任警察
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is why I joined the force
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the police
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,靠边停船  乱扔垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pull it over, litterbug
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱扔垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:36.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Litterbug?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下有逃犯抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:40.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got me a runner
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你这是在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.79,0:09:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都没驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a license anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.06,0:09:49.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:49.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:51.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(808,258)}安全驾驶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(738,206)}裤头村监狱
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.96,0:10:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关90天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,90 days
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(492,142)}市级法院
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.85,0:10:12.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你学到了教训  别乱扔垃圾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I hope you learned
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a valuable lesson about littering
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.97,0:10:14.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So long, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了喂小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to feed Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有时候会忘了喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.15,0:10:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sometimes you forget to feed him
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星坐牢肯定活不长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick can't survive in prison
Dialogue: 1,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他太软弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's too soft
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.36,0:10:23.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:23.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星是清白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's innocent
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我撕了派大星的驾照车窗抛物的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tore up Patrick's license and threw it out the window
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是乱丢垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the litterbug
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓我坐牢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take me, instead
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.36,0:10:35.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鉴于没有法律先例可循
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:35.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, considerin' there's no legal precedent
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关90天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,90 days
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.45,0:10:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,偿还了社会债务后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346,232)}裤头村监狱
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.23,0:11:03.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你驾考通过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.23,0:11:03.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you passed the test
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴你考到驾照了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.12,0:11:05.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you have a license
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.17,0:11:08.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要证明给你看  特地给你做了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:08.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And to prove it, I made you this
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:10.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(784,724)}裤头村\N一辈子好兄弟
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一辈子好兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.18,0:11:09.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pals forever
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它放到你船上吧  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's put it on your boatmobile, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早就没船了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have a boatmobile anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,船坏了  就扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:18.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It stopped workin', so I threw it away
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,指针指到了E
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The needle was on "e"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:20.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(888,920)}没油
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意思应该是结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I figured that must mean "end"
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那这个东西要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.72,0:11:25.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then what do we do with this?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样行不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's that?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了吗  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready, buddy?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready, pal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:45.85,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}土皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(245.316,450)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:48.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.74\pos(495.678,728)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:50.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(389.566,426)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:50.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.52\pos(515.736,678)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz29.29\pos(421.602,536)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.89,0:11:53.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.75,0:11:58.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:11:58.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您好  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.70,0:11:59.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good day, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.98,0:12:00.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:00.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可清楚你哪位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know exactly who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.49,0:12:07.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,878)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.27,0:12:07.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟小蜗共度黄金时光最美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:04.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,spending some quality time with my gar-gar
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杰森  实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jason, I have to be honest
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经有新欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's someone else
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Grandpa?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  救命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, help
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他来抓我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's on to me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:16.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:21.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,336)}里奇萨蒙斯健身指南
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:22.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得把这些书都烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to get rid of these books
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.55,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572,402)}如何阅读
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你看看为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll show you why
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见他没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:27.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See him?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他是图书馆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's from the library
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道我有书逾期了没还
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:31.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He knows about my overdue books
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以我就会被抓去坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which means I'm gonna get thrown in the big house
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道那是什么意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you know what that means
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,量小管饿的牢饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Small-portion meals?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, don't you worry
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我挺你到底
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got your back, man
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, there
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您好  年轻人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Salutations, young one
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您不会刚好认识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.55,0:12:50.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say, you wouldn't happen to know
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,住在这颗石头底下的海星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:52.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the starfish that lives under this rock, would you?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一只海星都不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I don't know any starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算我认识这位所谓的海星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even if I did know this "alleged" starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星也不会逾期不还图书馆的书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick wouldn't owe any overdue library books
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.80,0:13:04.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您不认识派大星可真是遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:04.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's too bad you don't know Patrick star
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我是一名宫廷成员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.43,0:13:06.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because I am from the royal ministry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有礼物要送他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:07.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and have a gift for him
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.31,0:13:10.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:10.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pretty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这简直是史上最难吃的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the worst-tasting gift, ever
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为那礼物是用来戴的  不是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's because you're supposed to wear it, not eat it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我给你看样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you something
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's here
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手上拿着的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What I hold in my hands
Dialogue: 1,0:13:27.85,0:13:30.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是张能追溯到好几世纪前的家谱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:30.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is a family tree that goes back centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(284,354)}变形虫王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1130,354)}霉菌后
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切起源于变形虫王与霉菌后的婚姻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It starts with the marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of king amoeba and queen mildew
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,历经数代近亲繁殖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:37.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then, through a few inbred generations
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,血统最终延续到了您  派大星阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:40.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ends at you, sir Patrick
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1092,788)}派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此您正是王室的后裔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which makes you a descendant of royalty
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,您就是王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are a king
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如今我将前去宫廷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:48.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, it's time I adjourned to the royal ministry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.64,0:13:52.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从此为您效劳  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.64,0:13:52.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where I shall be at your service, your highness
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.84,0:13:55.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, that's great
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.14,0:13:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你成国王了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That you're king
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么是国王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's a king?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.48,0:14:00.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当了国王就能要什么有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:00.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When you're a king, you can get anything you want
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要什么有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:01.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything I want?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.30,0:14:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你说咱能不能来点吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, do you think we could get somethin' to eat?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如你所愿  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your wish is my command, your majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位市民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good townspeople
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.87,0:14:17.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我们热烈欢迎新上任的国王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:17.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let us rejoice in welcoming our new king
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国王特别想要吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King needs food, badly
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是想干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this all abou-
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我帮你干嘛呢  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well, what can I do for you, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国王想要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:29.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The king would like-
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Zip it, SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟富哥讲话  你别插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm talking to the rich guy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要来十个蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have ten krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一杯蟹奶昔  大薯条
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:36.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a krabby milkshake, large fries
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有个更好的点子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got a better idea
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给国王量身定制的自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.07,0:14:45.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A buffet fit for a king
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tasty
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:49.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.85,0:14:52.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每个人的一生都要经历一段安定期
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.85,0:14:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There comes a time in every man's life
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when he's gotta settle down
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是找老婆  生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.90,0:14:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, get a wife, kids
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把自己的钱全送给岳父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:57.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a father-in-law you give all of your money to
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听着不错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That sounds great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能再来点番茄酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:01.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get a little more ketchup?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不然先给我付账得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's about you pay the check, instead?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No can do
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可是裤头村之王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As king of Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以要什么有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am allowed to have anything I want
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不对  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:13.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is correct
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要什么有什么  而且全免费
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything you want, and it's all free
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全免费
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All free?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁都别想在我蟹堡王吃霸王餐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody eats in me restaurant for free
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,管你是不是王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:21.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King or no king
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个你吃不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna eat that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打算吃  干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was planning to, why?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.54,0:15:27.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:27.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你哪来的特权  敢抢走我的吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What gives you the right to take my food?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟他说去  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:34.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell 'him, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  称王貌似不是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pat, I'm not sure if this is what being king is all about
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.35,0:15:40.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不是说我要什么有什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:40.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you said I could have anything I want
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.32,0:15:45.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最最好的朋友是在骗我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:45.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Was my bestest friend lying to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别闹了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不会骗你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never lie to you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟他说去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:51.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, tell him
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宫廷有令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By proclamation of the royal ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1084,488)}宫廷
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,国王有权要什么有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the king is entitled to get whatever he wants
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:01.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't fair
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人生本来就不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Life isn't fair, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你习惯去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get used to it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally did it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于集到了神奇太空鱼侠第二册
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At long last, I've acquired
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,issue number two of wonder space fish
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1146,362)}神奇\N太空鱼侠
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还全新未拆封
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.46,0:16:11.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And in mint condition
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下不惑之年可算圆满了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now my 40-year-old life
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,漫画书可也算是集齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my comic book collection are complete
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈一定会为我骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:17.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mom's gonna be so proud of me
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.40,0:16:22.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,骄个屁的傲  这些漫画书明明归我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:22.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, she won't be, because these comic books are mine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我一生都在收藏漫画书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I spent my entire life collecting those
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊  那你后半生给我哭丧去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:27.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well now you can spend
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the rest of your life crying about it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the king
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.10,0:16:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.85,0:16:32.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.85,0:16:32.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:33.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,cry about it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找我老妈哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cry right to my mom
Dialogue: 1,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱称王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love being king
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  感谢先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK, thank you, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星肯定需要这个助步器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure king Patrick could use this walker
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但愿如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope so
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连海神王都知道我需要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:24.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune knows I did
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:26.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是的  阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, sire?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你给点意见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need your opinion on something
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得这平板电视
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think the giant flat screen TV
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是应该搬到高贵蛋雕陈列那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,should go over the fancy egg display
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.94,0:17:41.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是室内游泳池那边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.94,0:17:41.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or the indoor swimming pool?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, sunshine
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多美的早晨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:59.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful morning
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.97,0:18:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:14.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,往后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.57,0:18:18.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's good
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:20.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么  可可可我家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What, but, but, but, my house
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我家是怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's happened to my-
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:32.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:35.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the barnacles is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看你们干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at what you've done
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看我家前院糟蹋成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.08,0:18:39.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at my poor front yard
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就你家前院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your front yard?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,殿下正在建造一个皇家摩天轮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His royal highness is building a royal Ferris wheel
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,摩天轮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ferris wheel?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, isn't it great?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,棒个屁  烂到没边了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, it's not great, it's horrible
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我得了  停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村的居民们  停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:52.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,People of Bikini Bottom, stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.67,0:18:53.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:53.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星不是国王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:55.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick's no king
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这一坨粉东西  能当什么王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:58.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can this pink blob be king?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.50,0:19:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你  难道真的相信那只无脑海星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.50,0:19:02.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, can you honestly believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that mindless starfish
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能称得上什么王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,coud possibly be the king of anything?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,土皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King of morons
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.90,0:19:10.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:10.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He might be on to somethin'
Dialogue: 1,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:13.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看  看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:15.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,see, see, see, see
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  凭什么要把自己家当都给他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why are we givin' this guy all of our stuff?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看吧  看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, see?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你才不是王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:27.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not a king
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别人也都这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now they all think so, too
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:33.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:34.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.07,0:19:36.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, get him
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就此下令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:44.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I decree
Dialogue: 1,0:19:44.75,0:19:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.75,0:19:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Attack
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得令  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right away, your majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:50.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.49,0:19:51.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:51.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可不可以请你签下这份条约
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.67,0:19:53.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I get you to sign this treaty
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.32,0:19:55.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,承诺永远效忠派大星国王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:55.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,promising your eternal loyalty to king Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.55,0:19:56.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:56.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,条约是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.83,0:19:58.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A treaty, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我对你条约的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here's what I think of your treaty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的臣民抛弃了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My royal subjects have deserted me
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都怪那个垃圾章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.52,0:20:09.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And it's all 'cause of that horrible Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是他的错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is all his fault
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怪他  怪他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His, his
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不怪我  怪他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,not mine, his
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what's happened to you?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不懂你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.35,0:20:21.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.57,0:20:25.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, actually
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.29,0:20:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板估计不知道我跑哪了  然后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs is probably wondering where I am, and-
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:28.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and what?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.52,0:20:34.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  就只是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:34.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, well, it's just that, um
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你有点乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:37.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're kind of being a jerk
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还以为你要说我滥用权力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:45.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to say I was abusing my power
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I-
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁说我滥用权力了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's saying I'm abusing my power?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要抓全镇居民你去坐牢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll put the whole town in prison
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敢质疑我权威  就是叛国
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:58.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Questioning my authority is treason
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.66,0:21:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傻傻演说老半天  渴死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.66,0:21:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All these giggly speeches are making me thirsty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  给我来点喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I request a drink
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.27,0:21:07.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.27,0:21:07.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:11.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家都走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, everybody's gone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.30,0:21:17.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm all alone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  我自个找喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:19.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll get it myself
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,敲敲门
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Knock, knock
Dialogue: 1,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要讲敲门笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A knock-knock joke
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:27.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:29.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是你  你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm you, and you are me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.79,0:21:38.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我变什么玩意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:38.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What have I become?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有畜生  畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A monster, monster
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.76,0:21:45.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:45.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's, it's you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  你拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, here, take it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我再也不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want it anymore
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它害我变畜生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's turned me into a monster
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.17,0:21:54.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:54.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I know what's going on here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.04,0:21:58.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  能力越大责任就越大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:21:58.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, with great power comes great responsibility
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不懂我刚说的大道理  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You haven't a clue what I just told you, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.06,0:22:02.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.06,0:22:02.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, just as well
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是来取回王冠的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:07.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've come to take the crown back
Dialogue: 1,0:22:07.34,0:22:11.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,似乎到头来你也并不是王室成员
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:11.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as it would seem that you aren't royalty after all
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我发现家谱上面沾了咖啡渍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I discovered this coffee stain
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它清干净就能看出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:17.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which, upon removal, reveals
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.41,0:22:20.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗阁下才是真正的王位继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.41,0:22:20.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that sir Gary is the true heir to the king's crown
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(542,900)}小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:22.77,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1202,776)}小蜗
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.77,0:22:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.77,0:22:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, would you look at that
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  你称王了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:26.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, you're royalty
